    "---\n",
    "### Question 6\n",
    "\n",
    "Créer une variable **`surrepresentation`** qui compare, en relatif, les scores nationaux et départementaux.\n",
    "\n",
    "Par exemple, si un candidat a un score de 30% dans un département mais de 15% ailleurs, la valeur de `surrepresentation` sera égale à **100 (%)**."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "5529bc5f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Question 6\n",
    "\n",
    "score_departements['surrepresentation'] = (\n",
    "    (score_departements['score_departement'] - score_departements['score_national'])\n",
    "    / score_departements['score_national']\n",
    "    * 100\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
